    "note": "<p>In the first sample case desired sequences are:</p><p><span class=\"tex-span\">1:\u20091</span>; <span class=\"tex-span\"><i>m</i><sub class=\"lower-index\">1</sub>\u2009=\u20090</span>;</p><p><span class=\"tex-span\">2:\u20091,\u20092</span>; <span class=\"tex-span\"><i>m</i><sub class=\"lower-index\">2</sub>\u2009=\u20091</span>;</p><p><span class=\"tex-span\">3:\u20091,\u20093</span>; <span class=\"tex-span\"><i>m</i><sub class=\"lower-index\">3</sub>\u2009=\u2009|3\u2009-\u20091|\u2009=\u20092</span>.</p><p>In the second sample case the sequence for any intersection <span class=\"tex-span\">1\u2009&lt;\u2009<i>i</i></span> is always <span class=\"tex-span\">1,\u2009<i>i</i></span> and <span class=\"tex-span\"><i>m</i><sub class=\"lower-index\"><i>i</i></sub>\u2009=\u2009|1\u2009-\u2009<i>i</i>|</span>.</p><p>In the third sample case\u00a0\u2014 consider the following intersection sequences:</p><p><span class=\"tex-span\">1:\u20091</span>; <span class=\"tex-span\"><i>m</i><sub class=\"lower-index\">1</sub>\u2009=\u20090</span>;</p><p><span class=\"tex-span\">2:\u20091,\u20092</span>; <span class=\"tex-span\"><i>m</i><sub class=\"lower-index\">2</sub>\u2009=\u2009|2\u2009-\u20091|\u2009=\u20091</span>;</p><p><span class=\"tex-span\">3:\u20091,\u20094,\u20093</span>; <span class=\"tex-span\"><i>m</i><sub class=\"lower-index\">3</sub>\u2009=\u20091\u2009+\u2009|4\u2009-\u20093|\u2009=\u20092</span>;</p><p><span class=\"tex-span\">4:\u20091,\u20094</span>; <span class=\"tex-span\"><i>m</i><sub class=\"lower-index\">4</sub>\u2009=\u20091</span>;</p><p><span class=\"tex-span\">5:\u20091,\u20094,\u20095</span>; <span class=\"tex-span\"><i>m</i><sub class=\"lower-index\">5</sub>\u2009=\u20091\u2009+\u2009|4\u2009-\u20095|\u2009=\u20092</span>;</p><p><span class=\"tex-span\">6:\u20091,\u20094,\u20096</span>; <span class=\"tex-span\"><i>m</i><sub class=\"lower-index\">6</sub>\u2009=\u20091\u2009+\u2009|4\u2009-\u20096|\u2009=\u20093</span>;</p><p><span class=\"tex-span\">7:\u20091,\u20094,\u20095,\u20097</span>; <span class=\"tex-span\"><i>m</i><sub class=\"lower-index\">7</sub>\u2009=\u20091\u2009+\u2009|4\u2009-\u20095|\u2009+\u20091\u2009=\u20093</span>.</p>",
